AddressInfo.Title: Serenberry Vineyards
AddressInfo.AccessComments: It is right off-road near their metal winery building on a post and marked with an EV sign.

Connections.Comments: It is powered by the Winery building that is all Solar Powered.  This is for the guests that come out to the Tasting Barn and need to charge their vehicle or of course anyone along the way that finds themselves in need of some power.

GeneralComments: This is for the guests that come out to the Tasting Barn and need to charge their vehicle while they are there.  It is powered by the Winery building that is all Solar Powered.
